cts of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/149323/', '', 'Apomorphine, Fesoterodine, Pentosan polysulfate, Calcium chloride, Phenazopyridine, Sildenafil, Alprostadil, Acetohydroxamic acid, Yohimbine, Avanafil, Papaverine, More', 'Apomorphine, Pentosan polysulfate, Phenazopyridine, Alprostadil, Acetohydroxamic acid, Yohimbine, Avanafil, Papaverine, Phenyl salicylate, Oxybutynin, Magnesium hydroxide, More', 1767369485);
